{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9d3fc806c1","title":"对中央关于限期完成购粮计划的指示稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ddf8e66ffe","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"9d3fc806c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"6e661535a6","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央1953年5月10日关于限期完成购粮计划给东北局并告各中央局，中财委、中央商业部、粮食部党组的指示稿上。"},{"id":"69ad100c14","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央指示稿中最后一段话，这段话是：“中央同时同意你们采取卖粮买货者给以九七折优待办法，但对个体农民结合合同方式集中卖粮二吨以上者给以百分之五的优待，是否会有利富农、小贩，而使零散卖粮的农民得不到好处？请考虑。毛泽东在审阅时删去了这段话。"}],"contents":[{"id":"696a46d9f7","type":"title","text":"对中央关于限期完成购粮计划的指示稿的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1"},{"id":"6e661535a6","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1"},{"id":"69ad100c14","type":"paragraph","text":"为了得粮，使富农、小贩得些好处是可以的，文尾数句回可删去。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1"},{"id":"d7e644b782","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1"},{"id":"3a279c0686","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1"}],"page":{"id":"a8e57a6c40","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"9d3fc806c1","start":166,"end":166}}}},"__N_SSG":true}